author: adrianc
msg: Fixed problem with OFBiz script syntax versus UEL syntax. UEL identifiers cannot start with a digit, so identifiers created from IDs would generate syntax errors. This commit fixes that by converting ID identifiers internally by prefixing them with an underscore.
